        <abstract> 
<p>C. E. Bessey’s case [see <hi rend="doubleUnderline">10969</hi>] came too late, as the sheets had been printed, but CD thinks it should be carefully investigated as a possible case of incipient heterostyly.</p> 
            <p>Is trying to make out the function of "bloom", the waxy secretion on leaves and fruits.</p>
        </abstract>
